  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Anura Kumara is also in the running for the new interim president post",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "People's Liberation Front's leader Anura Kumara Dissanayake will also contest as a candidate for the new interim presidential post, said MP Vijitha Herath of the People's Liberation Front.",
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Thammika Dasanayake announced today that there is a vacancy for the post of President after the resignation of Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "In this case, it is noted that it has already been announced that President Ranil Wickremesinghe, United People's Shakti President Sajith Premadasa and Podujana Peramuna's Dulles Alagapperuma will contest for the new interim presidency."
      ],
